# Design Guidelines

## Design Principles

- **Mobile-First Responsive:** Design for mobile devices first, then scale up
- **Visual Content Focus:** Let photography and videography be the hero
- **Bold & Adventurous:** Design should reflect the brand's bold, adventurous spirit
- **Fast Performance:** Optimize for quick loading, especially for media-heavy content
- **Accessible:** Ensure design is accessible to all users

## Color Application

### Header
- **Background:** Dark/Black (`#000000`)
- **Text:** White (`#FFFFFF`)
- **Navigation:** High contrast for readability
- **Style:** Fixed or sticky header for easy navigation

### Background Sections
- **Primary Background:** Light Grey (`#D3D3D3`)
- **Usage:** Content sections, alternating backgrounds
- **Purpose:** Create visual separation and breathing room between content areas

### Call-to-Action Buttons
- **Color:** Red (`#C1272D`)
- **Style:** Bold, prominent, clearly visible
- **Usage:** Primary CTAs, contact buttons, inquiry buttons
- **Hover States:** Slightly darker red or subtle animation

### Text & Contrast
- **Primary Text:** Black (`#000000`) on light backgrounds
- **Secondary Text:** Dark grey on light backgrounds
- **Text on Dark:** White (`#FFFFFF`) on black/dark backgrounds
- **Ensure WCAG AA contrast ratios:** Minimum 4.5:1 for normal text, 3:1 for large text

## Layout Guidelines

### Mobile-First Approach

1. **Start with Mobile:** Design and develop for smallest screens first (320px+)
2. **Progressive Enhancement:** Add features and complexity as screen size increases
3. **Touch-Friendly:** Ensure all interactive elements are at least 44x44px
4. **Readable Text:** Minimum 16px font size for body text on mobile

### Responsive Breakpoints

- **Mobile:** 320px - 767px (primary focus)
- **Tablet:** 768px - 1023px
- **Desktop:** 1024px - 1439px
- **Large Desktop:** 1440px+

### Grid System

- **Mobile:** Single column layout
- **Tablet:** 2-column grid where appropriate
- **Desktop:** 3-4 column grid for galleries
- **Flexible:** Use CSS Grid and Flexbox for responsive layouts

## Component Specifications

### Header
- **Background:** Black (`#000000`)
- **Text:** White (`#FFFFFF`)
- **Height:** Compact on mobile, expandable navigation
- **Position:** Fixed or sticky for easy access
- **Logo:** Prominent, clear branding

### Hero Section
- **Full-width:** Edge-to-edge on all devices
- **Content:** Bold headline, compelling imagery/video
- **CTA:** Red button (`#C1272D`) prominently placed
- **Mobile:** Stack content vertically, ensure readability

### Content Sections
- **Background:** Alternate between white and light grey (`#D3D3D3`)
- **Padding:** Generous spacing (mobile: 1rem, desktop: 2-3rem)
- **Max Width:** Content containers max-width for readability

### Gallery Components
- **Mobile:** Single column, full-width images
- **Tablet:** 2-column grid
- **Desktop:** 3-column grid
- **Spacing:** Consistent gaps between items
- **Lazy Loading:** Implement for performance

### Forms
- **Inputs:** Clear borders, adequate padding
- **Labels:** Visible, accessible
- **Submit Button:** Red (`#C1272D`) CTA button
- **Error States:** Clear, accessible error messaging
- **Mobile:** Full-width inputs, stacked layout

### Footer
- **Background:** Black (`#000000`) or dark grey
- **Text:** White (`#FFFFFF`)
- **Links:** Clear, accessible
- **Mobile:** Stack columns vertically

## Visual Hierarchy

1. **Primary:** Hero sections, main CTAs (Red buttons)
2. **Secondary:** Section headers, navigation
3. **Tertiary:** Body content, supporting information
4. **Use size, color, and spacing** to establish clear hierarchy

## Spacing System

- **Consistent Units:** Use rem or px consistently
- **Mobile Padding:** 1rem (16px) minimum
- **Desktop Padding:** 2-3rem (32-48px)
- **Section Spacing:** 3-4rem between major sections
- **Element Spacing:** 1-2rem between related elements

## Image & Media Guidelines

- **Optimization:** Compress all images, use modern formats (WebP, AVIF)
- **Responsive Images:** Use srcset for different screen sizes
- **Lazy Loading:** Implement for below-the-fold content
- **Video:** Optimize file sizes, provide fallback images
- **Alt Text:** Always include descriptive alt text for accessibility

## Interaction Design

- **Hover States:** Clear feedback on interactive elements
- **Focus States:** Visible focus indicators for keyboard navigation
- **Transitions:** Smooth, subtle animations (200-300ms)
- **Loading States:** Show loading indicators for async content
- **Error Handling:** Clear error messages and recovery paths
